data.eml:eml: A new species of the genus Malaisemyia Alexander from China, with an updated key to the world species (Diptera, Pediciidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Mao, Meng, Yang, Ding (2010): A new species of the genus Malaisemyia Alexander from China, with an updated key to the world species (Diptera, Pediciidae). Zootaxa 2502: 56-60, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.195852
